User case: Next level extends MaxSizeUC

Summary: when player reaches max size the game moves on to the next level 
		 as well as increasing difficulty
		 
Priority: low

Normal flow 1: reach max size
	User action		|		System action
	
1.1							pause the game
							
1.2							zoom out the camera so 
							that the player look small
							again and display "next level"
							
1.3							increase the difficulty
							
1.4							resume the game